<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2398] Improve tests to work easier from IDEs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2398</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;As reported by Paolo Castagna on the mailing lists, some tests fail when you run them from eclipse.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some of the failures he reports are actually code problems such as base test classes not being &lt;br/&gt;
abstract when they should be... we should fix things like that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
